definitions.definition: Each of the two large fleshy halves of the posterior part of the body between the base of the back , the perineum , and the top of the legs .
The convexity of a ship behind , under the stern .

main_definition: ( usually in the plural ) Each of the two large fleshy halves of the posterior part of the body between the base of the back , the perineum , and the top of the legs .
secondary_definitions: ( nautical ) The convexity of a ship behind , under the stern .
